Package at.tfr.pfad.view

Class MailTemplateBean

java.lang.Object
at.tfr.pfad.view.BaseBean<MailTemplate>
at.tfr.pfad.view.MailTemplateBean
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Named @ViewScoped public class MailTemplateBean extends BaseBean<MailTemplate> implements Serializable
Backing bean for MailTemplate entities. This class provides CRUD functionality for all MailTemplate entities. It focuses purely on Java EE 6 standards (e.g. @ConversationScoped for state management, PersistenceContext for persistence, CriteriaBuilder for searches) rather than introducing a CRUD framework or custom base class.
